    We'll dive into the root problem, how it
    was solved for, and pull back to look at how it evovled. The we'll dive
    into an end state of one of the lines of work.
  </p>

  <p>
    As a director, my role was to ensure that the team has buy in, support space
    to explore, a vetted direction and the best path forward.
    <mark>My role is to derisk our time-investment by ensuring that we are
    solving an important and impactful problem with the right solution.</mark>
    I hold myself and my teams accountable.
  </p>

