  </h2>

  <p>
    I love the double diamond.
    This is the process I will bring to a team if they don't have one.
    <mark>If they have a process, I’ll be sure to push for
    a process that incorporates the key elements
    — the problem must be real, and the solution tested.</mark>
    This was the foundation I lay for my teams, and for the team solving
    this problem.
  </p>
  <p>
    But at first, our problem was too big and we needed a short
    learning cycle. So, I pulled from another tool in my toolset.
  </p>

